## Searching Flight [/api/flight{?departure,arrival,depart,number_of_person}]

Provide a list of flight.

+ Parameters
    + departure (string) - city of department
    + arrival (string) - destination
    + depart (date) - date of department
    + number_of_person (number) - number of person

### List Flight with Conditions [GET]
+ Response 200

        [
            {
                "flight_id": "abcdef",
